+# Morning Light — Image & Asset Prompts
+
+> Warm, grounded, and quietly confident. Like a deep breath before the day begins.
+
+---
+
+## Logo Concepts
+
+**Primary Wordmark:**
+A wordmark reading "SAGE" in Fraunces serif, weight 600. Letterspacing slightly open (+2%). The "S" has a subtle leaf vein running through its curve — organic, not literal. Color: Sage Moss (#4A7C59) on white. No tagline in the logo itself.
+
+**Icon Mark:**
+A single stylized leaf, slightly abstracted — the veins form a gentle conversation-bubble silhouette. Filled Sage Moss (#4A7C59). Rounded corners, feels hand-drawn but precise. Works at 24px and 512px.
+
+**Logo Animation:**
+The leaf icon fades in from 80% scale with a gentle spring (cubic-bezier 0.34, 1.2, 0.64, 1) over 600ms. The wordmark letters appear left-to-right with a staggered 40ms delay, each fading up from 8px below. Total duration: ~900ms. Feels like a morning stretch — unhurried, natural.
+
+---
+
+## Social Media Posts
+
+**Instagram Grid Post — Parenting Tip:**
+Warm parchment background (#F7F3EE). Large Fraunces serif headline at top: "Bedtime doesn't have to be a battle." Body text in Plus Jakarta Sans below, 2–3 lines of advice. Small Sage Moss leaf icon in bottom-left corner. Thin Golden Hour (#F2C46D) horizontal rule separating headline from body. No photo — pure typography. Generous whitespace. Aspect ratio 1:1, 1080×1080px.
+
+**Instagram Story — Quick Tip:**
+Full-bleed soft photograph of a parent's hands holding a child's hand (shot from above, natural light, slightly warm grade). Overlay: semi-transparent Parchment (#F7F3EE) card in the lower third with rounded corners (16px). Card contains Fraunces italic heading and Plus Jakarta Sans body tip. Sage Moss leaf icon top-left of card. Swipe-up CTA in Warm Clay (#C97B4B). 1080×1920px.
+
+**Twitter/X Header:**
+Horizontal composition. Left half: Fraunces headline "Parent with confidence, every day." in Sage Moss on Parchment. Right half: soft botanical illustration — loose, muted green and clay tones, abstract leaf forms at 20% opacity. Clean dividing line. 1500×500px.
+
+**Facebook Cover:**
+Wide parchment field. Centered Sage wordmark. Below: tagline "Your personalized AI parenting partner" in Plus Jakarta Sans, Slate Earth (#2E3830). Subtle radial gradient of Fern (#6FA884) at 8% opacity behind the text. 820×312px.
+
+---
+
+## Web Landing Page
+
+**Hero Section:**
+Full-width, generous vertical padding (120px top, 160px bottom). Parchment (#F7F3EE) background. Centered layout.
+- Eyebrow: "MEET SAGE" in Plus Jakarta Sans, 12px uppercase, tracking 0.12em, Warm Clay color
+- Headline: "Parent with confidence, every day." in Fraunces, 56px/700, Slate Earth
+- Subhead: 2 sentences in Plus Jakarta Sans, 20px, Slate Earth at 70% opacity
+- CTA button: "Chat with Sage — It's Free" in Plus Jakarta Sans 16px/600, white text on Sage Moss, 12px radius, subtle shadow
+- Below CTA: a phone mockup screenshot of the Sage chat interface, tilted 2° with a soft drop shadow, floating on a radial gradient of Fern/Parchment
+
+**Social Proof Bar:**
+Thin horizontal strip. Warm White (#FDFAF7) background. Logos of press mentions or "Trusted by 10,000+ parents" in Plus Jakarta Sans, 14px, centered. Linen (#E8E0D5) top/bottom borders.
+
+**Feature Section:**
+3-column grid on Warm White. Each column:
+- Icon (Phosphor filled, 32px, Sage Moss)
+- Heading in Fraunces, 22px
+- Body in Plus Jakarta Sans, 16px, 2 lines
+- No borders, shadow-only card depth
+
+**Testimonial Section:**
+Single large quote on Parchment. Fraunces italic, 28px, centered. Attribution in Plus Jakarta Sans, 14px. Warm Clay accent on the quotation mark (decorative, oversized, 120px, 10% opacity behind).
+
+---
+
+## Patterns
+
+**Botanical Micro-Pattern:**
+Tiny, scattered leaf silhouettes at 4% opacity on Parchment. Leaves are abstracted to 3–4 simple curved strokes. Random rotation. Tile size: 200×200px. Use on section backgrounds and email headers.
+
+**Dot Grid:**
+Linen (#E8E0D5) dots at 6% opacity on Parchment, 20px grid spacing. Use sparingly on neutral content sections. Feels like graph paper for journaling.
+
+**Gradient Mesh:**
+Soft, organic blobs — radial gradients of Fern (#6FA884) at 10% opacity and Warm Clay (#C97B4B) at 6% opacity. Overlapping ellipses, blurred, on Parchment. Use as decorative layer behind hero content. Never sharp edges.
+
+---
+
+## Icons
+
+**Style Direction:**
+Phosphor Icons, filled variant. Sage Moss (#4A7C59) default color. 2px visual weight at 24px size. Rounded terminals. Never outlined-only — always carry visual weight.
+
+**Custom Icon Set (if extending beyond Phosphor):**
+Consistent 24px grid. 2px stroke with rounded caps. Fill on key states (active, selected). Slight organic imperfection — corners are rounded at 3px, not perfectly geometric. Suggested custom icons: Milestone flag, Sleep moon, Feeding bottle, Routine calendar, Growth chart.
+
+---
+
+## Imagery
+
+**Photography Direction:**
+Real, unposed moments of parents and children. Warm natural light (golden hour preferred). Slightly desaturated — not oversaturated Instagram-style. Quiet, in-between moments: a parent reading, a child exploring, hands together.
+
+- Avoid: staged smiles, stock-photo perfection, clinical settings
+- Favor: messy kitchens, half-read books, grass stains, genuine expressions
+- Color grade: warm, slightly faded, matte finish. Shadows lifted. Never harsh contrast.
+- Crop: generous negative space. Off-center subjects. Room to breathe.
+
+**Illustration Direction (if used):**
+Bold, reduced forms. Think linocut or woodblock aesthetic — not watercolor, not vector-cute. Earthy palette: Sage Moss, Warm Clay, Golden Hour. Intentional imperfection in lines. Subjects: abstract parent-child silhouettes, botanical elements, simple objects (cups, books, toys). Never cartoonish or infantile.
+
+**Image Treatments:**
+- Rounded corners: 16px on all image containers
+- Subtle warm overlay: multiply blend of Parchment at 5% over photos
+- Shadow beneath images: var(--shadow-card)
+- No borders on images — shadow-only framing
